{"tid":1876563,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[工程撚入] 一個武漢肺炎就明點解港燈被人話狗也不屌","createTime":"2020-02-12T12:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T23:44:13.000Z","uid":255856,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3dd62398c43d35dd9caab3e77d7700424027cc07","tid":1876563,"uid":255856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:58:30.000Z","msg":"過完年中半山就大部分work from home, 山卡啦就話operational所以死人都要返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n安全第一喺工作之上完全係廢話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n膠層離地得太耐，日日揸住架攔路虎返工完全唔知出面班伙記係點逼火車地鐵巴士返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n公司喺山邊仲夠膽死叫人早一個鐘頭7點幾返到公司就係彈性上班，咁就可以咁俾你早收一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返山卡啦仲要冇交通工具提供，要你自己行路返公司，真係多撚謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人split office佢split office, split完2條team又要日日一齊b fing, 咁split嚟做乜柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返工搭車搭𨋢食飯係咪唔算同一空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n分完team坐公司車就前排開始數落去坐一team, 另一team就車尾坐返上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做乜9呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />架公主號係咪住唔同層d乘客可以落船呀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同事有remote access又唔俾人work from home, 就係因為唔想同個外行嘅腦細解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗搏紮就咩屎撟都諗得出，攞班細嘅條命嚟較非，人渣之中呢d都算極品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時腦細一句，無論幾無道理幾唔make sense都成班狗咁仆去奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n公司出錢請你班膠層返嚟淨係識奶咁我請班腦殘藍絲都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係喎，唔記得咗班膠層大部分都係藍撚到紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔想再有確診，但係如果有，希望確診嘅係呢d腦殘膠層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e450e0d6704ebc889bd9b96c88716c71cc74eaf","tid":1876563,"uid":15235,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f2723e7c6e21bd81471e98294bb1312a5abbc7","tid":1876563,"uid":18214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e450e0d6704ebc889bd9b96c88716c71cc74eaf","tid":1876563,"uid":15235,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55dc50dd3e34b621982433f3ff35225e780b8fe","tid":1876563,"uid":255856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74f2723e7c6e21bd81471e98294bb1312a5abbc7","tid":1876563,"uid":18214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e450e0d6704ebc889bd9b96c88716c71cc74eaf","tid":1876563,"uid":15235,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241220ed947fced59f7bce179e057b2725a286dc","tid":1876563,"uid":17